7 Kraftwerk song, "Europe Endless": hierarchies prevail in European public and political life even as tolerance is touted by politicians and pundits as one of Europe’s chief virtues.School of Europeanness shows how post–Cold War liberalization projects in Latvia contributed to the current crisis of political liberalism in Europe, providing deep ethnographic analysis of the power relations in Latvia and the rest of Europe, and identifying the tension between exclusive polities and inclusive values as foundational of Europe’s political landscape.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aLiberalismzLatvia. 0aMinoritieszLatvia. 0aPost-communismzLatvia. 0aTolerationxPolitical aspectszLatvia. 4aAnthropology. 4aPolitical Science & Political History. 4aWest European History. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aEastern Europe, nationalism, liberalism, postsocialism, minorities, migration.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311060655308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics and Social Sciences 2018 Englishz978311060401608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781501716867?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501716867423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501716867/original  a978-3-11-060401-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Economics and Social Sciences 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060655-3  C